text: == Events == * Edmund I of England became King of England * July 14 – Pope Stephen VIII succeeds Pope Leo VII as the 127th pope. * Arabs lose Madrid to the Kingdom of León. == Births == * Emperor Romanos II of the Byzantine Empire * Emperor Taizong of Song == Deaths == * October 2 – Gilbert, Duke of Lorraine * October 27 – Æthelstan, King of the English
